data.description: As soon as you walk in to the south facing end unit, you will think to yourself "this is it!" Nestled in the attendance area of the Blue Ribbon Award Winning Rush Creek Elementary, this supremely updated townhome has the epitome of the wow factor. It features 9' ceilings recessed lighting, stainless appliances, 42" cabinets, updated flooring, contemporary paint and trim, a slate surround gas fireplace, an upper level with a loft, huge master bedroom with walk in closet, laundry and a huge bath with dual sinks and updated faucets.  All this in the best location in the neighborhood. It faces south, into a beautiful wetland area, not other townhouses! The association is financially strong, and the dues include homeowner's insurance! You will love to call this wonderful place home!
